data.revised_prompt: Create a vivid image of a domestic cat lounging peacefully. The cat should have a beautiful coat of fur in varying shades of ginger and a pair of clear, bright green eyes displaying a gentle demeanor. Its long tail is curled around its plump body, as it lays on a beautifully woven rug in a relaxed position. In the background, have a window revealing a tranquility inducing mid-day landscape.
